.name
SculptTools
.author
Bruce Thomson 
.description
Programs to create objects for use in Sculpt 4D.  Includes Brush_4D to
convert IFF brushes to objects in full color with HAM and EHB support and
wrap to various shapes (update to version on disk 361), Fractal_4d to
create fractal mountains with various coloring from brush, checkers or
based on altitude, and Spiral_4d to create a variety of objects based
around tubes and helixes.  
